</nav></header><main aria-label="main content"><div class="speakable">
      <b data-is-speakable>How To Manage Coronavirus Anxiety: Life Kit</b>   <b data-is-speakable>Shame spirals, toilet paper panic and bingeing on news — it's easy to worry, but harder to stop. Psychiatrist Judson Brewer explains why panic can be as contagious as a virus and shares simple ways to recenter yourself when you get carried away by anxious thoughts.</b>
